text: Yoshio Miyake (7 December 1913 - 26 April 1983) was a Japanese gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1913 births Category:1983 deaths Category:Japanese male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Japan Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
